Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.73,0:00:06.36,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Open your mind. Open your mind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.61,0:00:22.82,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Far beyond the deep blue Earth,\nyou and I shall meet...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.82,0:00:24.19,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...as a gentle breeze goes by.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.19,0:00:28.19,AMG TITLE,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,AH! MY GODDESS
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.19,0:00:29.66,AMG TITLE,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,AH! MY GODDESS
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.66,0:00:36.80,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A snow-white feather will come\nfluttering down, swaying gently in the air.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.80,0:00:43.91,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Without holding back, I want to\nenvelope you, my one and only love.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.91,0:00:53.32,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know I have the power to protect\nthe one I love, right here in my hands.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.32,0:01:00.06,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Open your mind.\NJust as I've always dreamed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.06,0:01:06.96,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let the wind carry off\nyour hopes, faraway.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.96,0:01:13.74,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have wings nobody can see.\NLook, you have them, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.74,0:01:22.05,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They'll take us to where we can be free.\NAnyone can be free.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.05,0:01:26.54,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The sky is so blue...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.62,0:01:34.59,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.13,0:01:37.16,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.16,0:01:41.20,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing. It's just that I feel\nso pathetic, looking like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.20,0:01:44.07,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to go back to normal soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.07,0:01:48.17,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Do you? But Keiichi,\nI think you're quite lovely.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.17,0:01:50.44,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the point, see...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.44,0:01:54.28,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I'm looking like this,\nI can't even show myself outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.28,0:01:57.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't been to class in 3 days now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.38,0:01:58.94,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.05,0:02:02.61,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.05,0:02:05.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like you to let me handle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.02,0:02:11.48,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi, sorry to keep you waiting!\NThis will turn you back to normal!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.48,0:02:13.16,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.16,0:02:18.04,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think? You won't stand out\nin these clothes, no matter where you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.04,0:02:20.94,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, that's not the point...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.94,0:02:24.74,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You mean you'd prefer\na different style of clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.74,0:02:26.28,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No, no...what I mean is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.28,0:02:27.48,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There!{\i0}\NNo, no...what I mean is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.41,0:02:30.44,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How sweet!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.02,0:02:33.25,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What is she doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.25,0:02:39.51,AMG episode name black,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ah! What Wouldn't I Give for\nan Angel With White Wings?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.39,0:02:44.88,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, I appreciate it. I'm so much\nmore comfortable as a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.88,0:02:48.27,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, now you owe me big time, Keiichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.27,0:02:51.10,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But you're the one\nwho made that potion, Urd!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.10,0:02:53.80,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But it was Skuld who made you take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.21,0:03:02.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is that Belldandy singing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.01,0:03:04.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Along with Holy Bell...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.65,0:03:10.25,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, what exactly\nis an angel to a goddess?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.25,0:03:12.96,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, to put it simply,\nshe's there for support.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.96,0:03:16.33,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There are some high-level magical spells\nthat can't be cast without an angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.33,0:03:17.65,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.65,0:03:22.67,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And also, the angel is like a symbol\nfor a goddess's soul and condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.67,0:03:27.73,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see, when Belldandy got sick,\nit affected her angel, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.73,0:03:29.91,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.91,0:03:33.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Every full-fledged goddess\nhas her own angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.01,0:03:36.34,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,So then you have one, too, Urd.\NAn angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.58,0:03:38.21,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.67,0:04:05.80,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.34,0:04:08.08,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Skuld.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.08,0:04:11.62,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That was so...\nthat was so beautiful just now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.62,0:04:14.61,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Your singing, and Holy Bell's too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.61,0:04:15.92,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.92,0:04:18.99,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Big Sister...um...uh, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.99,0:04:20.09,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.09,0:04:22.76,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the thing is...um...I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.76,0:04:25.90,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I was thinking I'd like an angel, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.90,0:04:26.80,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.80,0:04:32.37,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're not a full-fledged\ngoddess\nuntil you have your own angel, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.37,0:04:35.44,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait to be just\nlike you, Big Sister, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.44,0:04:37.24,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm proud of you, Skuld!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.24,0:04:38.14,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh?{\i0}\nI'm proud of you, Skuld!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.14,0:04:41.65,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You've found your sense of\nresponsibility as a goddess!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.65,0:04:44.42,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Well, not exactly, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.42,0:04:46.85,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We'd better start your training at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.85,0:04:47.72,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh?{\i0}\NWe'd better start your training at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.72,0:04:48.82,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to have an angel like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.82,0:04:51.52,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You've decided to take this seriously!{\i0}\nI just want to have an angel like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.52,0:04:51.99,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to have an angel like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.99,0:04:55.03,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As your older sister, I can't be happier.{\i0}\nI just want to have an angel like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.03,0:04:57.99,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What shall we have you practice first?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.66,0:05:03.17,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I am the goddess of the Pillar that\ncontrols\nthe workings of Heaven and Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.17,0:05:08.11,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I bid you now in my name, release\nyourself from the chains of the earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.11,0:05:09.91,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...that bind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.91,0:05:11.00,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.08,0:05:15.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There! There! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.01,0:05:18.25,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No one has ever mastered this\nwithout some difficulty at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.25,0:05:22.42,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. If you just keep working\nat it, I know you'll be able to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.42,0:05:23.49,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.49,0:05:25.12,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Behold!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.12,0:05:25.99,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'll use a Gravity Canceller Magnum!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.99,0:05:30.25,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You mustn't use a device like that!{\i0}\nI'll use a Gravity Canceller Magnum!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.43,0:05:35.57,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I did it! That's what you wanted\nme to do, right, Big Sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.57,0:05:40.57,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Magic is a power that comes from within.\NYou mustn't depend on outside sources.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.57,0:05:45.71,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm not like you, Big Sister.\nI don't have any talent for magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.71,0:05:48.25,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But isn't that why we're practicing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.25,0:05:49.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Urd!{\i0}\NBut isn't that why we're practicing?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.28,0:05:53.72,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Only those who have achieved\ntheir goals can talk about talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.72,0:05:55.79,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't accomplished anything yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.79,0:05:57.05,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.05,0:06:00.16,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All I want is to have\nan angel like Big Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.16,0:06:03.43,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It has nothing to do with\nwhether or not I can use magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.43,0:06:05.13,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yes it does.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.50,0:06:07.97,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Is that true, Big Sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.97,0:06:13.37,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. To have an angel, you must first\nhave enough power to support her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.37,0:06:17.14,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you must practice magic\nspells, to enhance your power.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.14,0:06:18.68,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, is that right...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.68,0:06:22.91,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, it's 100 years\ntoo soon for you to have an angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.91,0:06:25.52,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Start practicing more diligently!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.52,0:06:28.82,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think you are? Butting\nin and acting like some hotshot!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.82,0:06:30.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I am a hotshot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.59,0:06:37.06,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,See that? It's a piece of cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.06,0:06:40.23,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Grr! Then what about yours, Urd?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.23,0:06:42.07,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.07,0:06:48.21,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone who talks like such a hotshot\nmust have the most amazing angel ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.21,0:06:49.67,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Urd...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.18,0:06:56.98,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You bet I do! You can't even imagine\nhow magnificent this angel of mine is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.98,0:07:01.44,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I'm just way out of your\nleague, you know...out of your league!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.75,0:07:04.09,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I hate you, Urd!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.09,0:07:05.72,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Skuld!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.72,0:07:09.12,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What a little baby she is, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.86,0:07:12.33,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Urd!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.16,0:07:14.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.83,0:07:18.10,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just make sure you get Skuld\nto understand something...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.10,0:07:21.80,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...that having an angel isn't\nsomething to be taken lightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.80,0:07:23.07,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Urd!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.02,0:07:33.35,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Urd, are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.35,0:07:34.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.26,0:07:41.55,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we take a walk together?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.83,0:07:46.69,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right. I guess I'll join you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.69,0:07:48.26,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.91,0:08:05.28,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.85,0:08:08.48,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Urd...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.42,0:08:11.15,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.89,0:08:18.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.38,0:08:19.59,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.83,0:08:21.20,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The angel...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.20,0:08:22.57,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Urd!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.57,0:08:25.69,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,How did you feel when\nyou first got your angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.20,0:08:29.67,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.11,0:08:34.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I know I was scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.51,0:08:38.48,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You're still thinking about that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.48,0:08:41.08,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sorry I made you worry.{\i0}\NYou're still thinking about that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.99,0:08:43.42,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Urd!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.53,0:08:53.33,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She who is closest to me...\nwho knows me better than anyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.33,0:08:58.23,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She who is the mirror-image\nof my innermost soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.61,0:09:06.94,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Your angel is\nthe reflection of your soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.94,0:09:09.21,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Your other self...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.35,0:09:14.54,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth, angel!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.16,0:09:24.32,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Who am I kidding?\NOf course she wouldn't come out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.20,0:09:29.20,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Aha! This is my chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.20,0:09:33.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I thought something was fishy...\NUrd doesn't have an angel either!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.77,0:09:38.17,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That means if I can manage\nto get an angel before Urd does...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.01,0:09:43.28,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Too cool...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.28,0:09:46.72,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That would rock...\nthat would really, really rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.72,0:09:51.15,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right, then...I'm going to start\npracticing my magic spells again!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.15,0:09:52.65,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ta da!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.52,0:09:57.56,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,With the help of my Virtual Simulator\N''Mr. Heartthrob'' Model 156, I can...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.56,0:10:00.00,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...become a magician, starting today!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.00,0:10:02.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Training should be conducted\nin a scientific way, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.93,0:10:06.20,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why do I have to take part in this too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.20,0:10:07.67,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.67,0:10:12.60,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This simulator isn't just for magic...it has\na wide variety of applications.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.60,0:10:16.71,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to get my helmet\nback the way it was, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.71,0:10:21.42,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Stop whining. One has to make sacrifices\nin the name of scientific progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.42,0:10:22.91,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Switch on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.46,0:10:29.56,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Darn, that's a wicked curve!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.56,0:10:33.36,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh man, I missed the corner!\NNo, no...I'm not done yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.36,0:10:36.43,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I have yet to unleash my full power!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.50,0:10:41.63,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the king of Nekomi Ridge!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.64,0:10:46.51,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,My experiment was a success!\NJust look at the way Keiichi's acting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.51,0:10:49.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, I'll be\nusing magic in no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.78,0:10:51.48,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just you wait, Urd.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.48,0:10:56.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to show you what I can do\nwhen I really put my mind to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.08,0:11:23.85,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I did it! I finally got it to levitate!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.85,0:11:26.45,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. One more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.45,0:11:30.81,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing's levitating...what in the\nworld does she think she's doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.39,0:11:39.45,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I think of it, was there\na time when I was just like her?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.29,0:12:43.82,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pleased to meet you, Big Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.70,0:13:23.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I wished I could be just like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.97,0:14:06.58,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm remembering that day again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.58,0:14:10.14,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I know it's pointless,\nno matter how many times I look back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.29,0:14:19.74,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What was it that\NBelldandy said that day?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.79,0:14:24.66,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I didn't realize\nhow quiet it's become.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.80,0:14:27.90,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,She's hopeless!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.90,0:14:32.22,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All she has to do is train hard,\nand she'll get to meet her angel...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.54,0:14:37.87,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I guess I have no right to talk...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.65,0:14:44.51,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't I realize it sooner?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.51,0:14:49.49,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's the point of casting virtual magic\nif I can't use it in the real world?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.49,0:14:53.62,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,At this rate, I'm never going\nto be able to control an angel!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.62,0:14:56.86,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, weren't you going\nto show me up big time?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.86,0:15:00.43,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's just like I said...\nit's 100 years too soon for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.51,0:15:11.61,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, that's it!\nIt's the results that matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.61,0:15:16.81,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,As long as I learn to use some kind\nof really amazing magic, anything goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.81,0:15:20.18,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This time around, I'm beyond serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.05,0:15:23.18,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.69,0:15:27.29,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe I was such a moron.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.29,0:15:32.05,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why the heck did I run all the\nway up Nekomi Ridge for no reason?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.20,0:15:36.53,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.14,0:15:42.07,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-oh. So it finally died on me, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.04,0:15:46.70,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.95,0:15:53.68,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you don't have to\ntell me who was behind this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.32,0:15:56.81,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Done!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.89,0:16:02.79,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Now that I have this, I'm sure\nto get an angel before she does!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.79,0:16:05.69,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So that's the reason, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.69,0:16:08.77,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, please. I was just\nborrowing it for a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.77,0:16:11.19,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's this gigantic thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.19,0:16:14.44,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Just listen and be struck with awe!\NTa da!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.44,0:16:17.34,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Power Amp Alpha 707!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.34,0:16:19.94,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This device will amplify my powers...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.94,0:16:23.31,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...even supporting an angel will\nbe just a walk in the park for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.31,0:16:27.02,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't Belldandy tell you\nto stick to training?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.02,0:16:28.49,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.49,0:16:32.39,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need steady training when I\nhave the power of science at my\nfingertips.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.39,0:16:34.21,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Switch on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.79,0:16:39.46,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Alpha 707!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.73,0:16:45.03,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.03,0:16:46.23,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Urd!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.20,0:16:49.21,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.21,0:16:52.74,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is a high-level water spell...\NBut...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.34,0:16:54.81,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.81,0:16:58.01,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, she's just unconscious.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.25,0:17:02.29,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I see. It's that device\nthat's amplifying her power.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.29,0:17:06.02,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi, I'm going to\nopen up the wall now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.03,0:17:14.66,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's no good. The wind-elemental spell\nisn't strong enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.66,0:17:19.03,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The only way to break through that wall\nof water is with a fire-elemental spell!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.40,0:17:21.20,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Urd...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.20,0:17:22.66,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, I can't.{\i0}\NUrd...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.66,0:17:24.14,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Urd!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.14,0:17:27.91,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I know you haven't been using\nyour angel all this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.91,0:17:30.98,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But please, just this once!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.98,0:17:34.32,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that I don't use her.\nI can't use her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.32,0:17:35.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.39,0:17:41.86,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since I was a child,\nI've always suspected...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.86,0:17:44.86,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...that I might be\nhalf-goddess, half-demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.86,0:17:48.90,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I was a little scared\nwhen I swallowed the angel's egg.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.90,0:17:52.24,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But even so, deep down inside\nI expected it to happen...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.24,0:17:55.41,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...that an angel with pure\nwhite wings would emerge.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.41,0:17:57.87,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,But that's not what came to pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.87,0:18:02.75,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,And when I was confronted with reality,\nI couldn't stop myself from screaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.75,0:18:07.61,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,You heard me that day, didn't you?\N''Don't ever come out again!''
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.92,0:18:12.89,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't ever come out again!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.99,0:18:15.48,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Urd...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.96,0:18:19.40,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Angels must always\nobey their goddesses...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.40,0:18:23.10,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...so let's try to come up\nwith another way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.43,0:18:26.20,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Belldandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.20,0:18:27.73,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.73,0:18:30.40,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There's something wrong with Skuld!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.08,0:18:38.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,This is terrible! That device\ncan only force power out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.64,0:18:43.11,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't do something,\NSkuld will lose all of her powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.92,0:18:45.18,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Urd!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.32,0:18:52.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take back what I said. I'm the one\nwho ordered my angel never to appear\nagain.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.83,0:18:54.00,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Urd!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.00,0:18:56.37,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing I can do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.37,0:18:57.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Urd!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.84,0:19:09.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Believe in yourself, Urd.\nI know you'll be able to meet her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.05,0:19:15.92,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen that smile somewhere before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.79,0:19:24.39,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Urd!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.39,0:19:25.83,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'd forgotten, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.83,0:19:27.06,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What?{\i0}\nI'd forgotten, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.06,0:19:30.23,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Why I wanted to have an angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.27,0:19:34.20,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,That's right, I'd forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.20,0:19:37.57,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm pleased to meet you, Big Sister.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.34,0:19:42.17,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Because I wished I could be...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.45,0:19:45.52,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...just like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.52,0:19:47.68,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Like Belldandy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.18,0:19:52.42,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what you may look like,\nyou are my other self.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.76,0:19:56.06,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't ever come out again!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.06,0:19:58.93,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Belldandy...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.77,0:20:04.50,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You have such a lovely angel!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.50,0:20:07.33,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...for accepting me as I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.74,0:20:11.10,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth, World of Elegance!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.01,0:20:19.95,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We meet at last...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.45,0:20:23.68,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...my other self.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.16,0:20:30.56,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Consumed by fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.40,0:20:36.26,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm never going to\nlet you go again. Never!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.17,0:20:48.30,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Skuld, I hope you get\nto meet yours soon, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.58,0:20:56.22,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,An angel's egg...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.22,0:20:59.69,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that day isn't far off...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.69,0:21:03.78,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,...when she'll hear\nyour soul calling to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.36,0:21:05.73,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Skuld!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.73,0:21:10.37,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...hey! So you did\nhave an angel, too, Urd!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.37,0:21:14.97,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! Doesn't that annoy you?\NLook at us, look at us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.97,0:21:18.26,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Urd!\n{\i1}I don't think I can stand this!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.71,0:21:24.98,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Keiichi! Phone's ringing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.98,0:21:28.85,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, isn't anyone around?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.35,0:21:31.68,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.06,0:21:33.58,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.03,0:21:40.13,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,We're back. Huh?\NWhat's the matter, Urd?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.13,0:21:43.20,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Urd? What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.20,0:21:46.26,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? Oh...yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.77,0:21:48.96,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.96,0:21:50.57,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.57,0:21:54.58,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, um, that was the\NAlmighty on the phone...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.58,0:21:56.15,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,The Almighty?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.15,0:22:01.18,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,He's suspending Urd's license as\npunishment\nfor walking off the job the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.18,0:22:03.65,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Goddesses can get their licenses\nsuspended?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.65,0:22:04.79,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes.{\i0}\NGoddesses can get their licenses\nsuspended?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.79,0:22:09.19,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,During the suspension period, you\ncan't use your powers as a goddess.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.19,0:22:14.76,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Please don't go! My little angel!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.76,0:22:16.40,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,I finally got to see you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.40,0:22:18.94,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So that's the deal, huh?{\i0}\nI finally got to see you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.94,0:22:22.90,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I hate getting my license suspended!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.24,0:22:25.71,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Always believe in yourself and\nyour Dreams. You have a wing!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.71,0:22:30.58,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Always believe in yourself and\nyour Dreams. You have a wing!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.58,0:22:35.38,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I love you so much it hurts...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.38,0:22:40.85,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And it hurts me that\nI can't tell you how I feel.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.06,0:22:46.10,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You and I have matching hearts...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.10,0:22:51.23,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So we must share the\nsame scars deep down inside.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.23,0:22:56.67,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But now that I'm in your arms,\nI think I can catch...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.67,0:23:01.64,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...your pounding heartbeat this time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.64,0:23:07.15,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nobody else matters...\NAll we have to do is gaze at each other.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.15,0:23:12.56,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's all right for your heart to flutter...\NAll we have to do is love each other.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.56,0:23:17.55,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Open your heart, and\nride that favorable wind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.55,0:23:23.09,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't run away from happiness.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.70,0:23:28.60,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll always be waiting for you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.60,0:23:33.81,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So come rest your wings anytime.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.81,0:23:38.82,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's all right to cry...\nanytime you need to.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.82,0:23:44.45,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I just want to see you again...\NAll we have to do is love each other.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.45,0:23:49.43,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Open your heart, and\nride that favorable wind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.43,0:23:55.03,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I just want you to be happy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.90,0:23:59.57,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,A pure white soul clashes\nwith demon-black blood...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.57,0:24:03.54,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,When that balance is broken, she is\ntransformed into the Lord of Terror.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.54,0:24:07.04,AMG episode name,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode: Ah! The Devil's Whisper\NComing from an Urn?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.04,0:24:10.68,AMG,Comment,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-oh, look what's happening to my bike!
